` |\n26\t\n27\t## Extraction Rules\n28\t\n29\t### Colors\n30\t\n31\tFor every color entry like `\"Leaf Green (#58CC02) — primary action\"`:\n32\t- Use the **token name** from DESIGN.md as the CSS property name\n33\t- Prefix with `--color-`\n34\t\n35\t```css\n36\t/* From Color Palette table */\n37\t--color-primary: #58CC02;\n38\t--color-primary-dark: #46A302;\n39\t--color-surface: #F7F7F7;\n40\t--color-bg: #FFFFFF;\n41\t\n42\t/* Semantic colors */\n43\t--color-success: #58CC02;\n44\t--color-success-bg: #D7F5B1;\n45\t--color-error: #FF4B4B;\n46\t--color-error-bg: #FFD0D0;\n47\t```\n48\t\n49\t### Typography\n50\t\n51\tExtract font families and build the Google Fonts URL:\n52\t\n53\t```html\n54\t<link href=\"https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Nunito:wght@500;600;700&display=swap\" rel=\"stylesheet\" />\n55\t```\n56\t\n57\tMap to CSS custom properties:\n58\t\n59\t```css\n60\t--font-primary: 'Nunito', system-ui, -apple-system, sans-serif;\n61\t\n62\t/* Type scale */\n63\t--text-heading-xl-size: 28px;\n64\t--text-heading-xl-weight: 700;\n65\t--text-heading-xl-lh: 1.2;\n66\t\n67\t--text-body-size: 16px;\n68\t--text-body-weight: 600;\n69\t--text-body-lh: 1.5;\n70\t```\n71\t\n72\t### Spacing\n73\t\n74\t```css\n75\t--space-1: 4px;\n76\t--space-2: 8px;\n77\t--space-3: 12px;\n78\t--space-4: 16px;\n79\t--space-6: 24px;\n80\t--space-8: 32px;\n81\t```\n82\t\n83\t### Border Radius\n84\t\n85\t```css\n86\t--radius-sm: 8px;\n87\t--radius-md: 12px;\n88\t--radius-lg: 16px;\n89\t--radius-pill: 999px;\n90\t```\n91\t\n92\t### Shadows\n93\t\n94\t```css\n95\t--shadow-sm: 0 2px 4px rgba(0,0,0,0.08);\n96\t--shadow-md: 0 4px 12px rgba(0,0,0,0.12);\n97\t--shadow-lg: 0 8px 24px rgba(0,0,0,0.16);\n98\t```\n99\t\n100\t### Motion\n101\t\n102\t```css\n103\t--ease-bounce: cubic-bezier(0.34, 1.56, 0.64, 1);\n104\t--ease-out: cubic-bezier(0, 0, 0.2, 1);\n105\t--duration-fast: 150ms;\n106\t--duration-normal: 250ms;\n107\t--duration-slow: 400ms;\n108\t```\n109\t\n110\t### Device & Safe Areas\n111\t\n112\t```css\n113\t/* Mobile viewport */\n114\t--device-width: 375px;\n115\t--device-height: 812px;\n116\t\n117\t/* Touch targets (Material 3 minimum) */\n118\t--touch-min: 48px;\n119\t\n120\t/* Scaffold chrome heights */\n121\t--app-bar-height: 56px;\n122\t--bottom-nav-height: 80px;\n123\t--status-bar-height: 44px;\n124\t--home-indicator-height: 34px;\n125\t```\n126\t\n127\t## Flutter Token Mapping\n128\t\n129\tThe CSS tokens map to Flutter `AppTheme` constants and Material 3 theme properties:\n130\t\n131\t| CSS Token | Flutter Equivalent |\n132\t|-----------|-------------------|\n133\t| `--color-primary: #hex` | `ColorScheme.fromSeed(seedColor: Color(0xFF...))` |\n134\t| `--color-surface: #hex` | `ColorScheme.surface` |\n135\t| `--font-primary: 'Outfit'` | `GoogleFonts.outfit()` in `TextTheme` |\n136\t| `--radius-md: 12px` | `AppTheme.radiusMd = 12` |\n137\t| `--space-4: 16px` | `AppTheme.spaceMd = 16` |\n138\t| `--ease-bounce: cubic-bezier(...)` | `AppTheme.easeBounce = Cubic(...)` |\n139\t| `--duration-normal: 250ms` | `AppTheme.durationNormal = Duration(milliseconds: 250)` |\n140\t| `--touch-min: 48px` | Material 3 default (48dp minimum tap target) |\n141\t| `--app-bar-height: 56px` | `AppBar` default height |\n142\t| `--bottom-nav-height: 80px` | `NavigationBar` default height |\n143\t"}]},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"dac7715c-8af6-4c77-b4d3-56bf38d190c3","uuid":"95dce901-3889-4917-b4b0-fe541d78f854","timestamp":"2026-05-18T15:11:37.053Z","tool_use_result":{"type":"text","file":{"filePath":"/Users/minh/Documents/openplayboosks/examples/baby-app/.claude/skills/stitch-generate/references/reading-design-md.md","content":"# Reading a DESIGN.md\n\nHow to parse a DESIGN.md file and extract design tokens for mobile screen mockup generation. Tokens are expressed as CSS custom properties for browser preview, but map directly to Flutter's `AppTheme` constants.\n\n**Input:** `DESIGN.md` file (project design system)\n**Output:** `:root` CSS custom properties block (for preview) + Google Fonts `<link>` tag\n\n## Section Mapping\n\nA DESIGN.md contains up to 12 sections. Each maps to specific CSS custom properties:\n\n| DESIGN.md Section | CSS Output | Example |\n|---|---|---|\n| **Color Palette** | `--color-{name}: {hex}` | `--color-primary: #58CC02` |\n| **Typography** | `--font-{role}`, `--text-{size}` + Google Fonts URL | `--font-primary: 'Nunito', sans-serif` |\n| **Spacing System** | `--space-{n}: {value}` | `--space-4: 16px` |\n| **Border Radius** | `--radius-{size}: {value}` | `--radius-md: 16px` |\n| **Shadows & Elevation** | `--shadow-{level}: {value}` | `--shadow-sm: 0 2px 4px rgba(0,0,0,0.08)` |\n| **Motion & Animation** | `--ease-{name}`, `--duration-{name}` | `--ease-bounce: cubic-bezier(0.34, 1.56, 0.64, 1)` |\n| **Visual Theme** | Atmosphere dials inform layout density, motion intensity | Used as generation guidance, not direct tokens |\n| **Component Patterns** | Reference for HTML structure and state classes | Informs element markup |\n| **Anti-Patterns** | Banned patterns list | Quality gate during generation |\n| **Device & Safe Areas** | Phone viewport, safe area insets, status bar | `--device-width: 375px`, `--touch-min: 48px` |\n| **Iconography** | Icon style, stroke width, sizes | Informs inline SVG specs |\n| **Accessibility** | Contrast, touch targets, motion preferences | Informs ARIA + `prefers-reduced-motion` |\n\n## Extraction Rules\n\n### Colors\n\nFor every color entry like `\"Leaf Green (#58CC02) — primary action\"`:\n- Use the **token name** from DESIGN.md as the CSS property name\n- Prefix with `--color-`\n\n```css\n/* From Color Palette table */\n--color-primary: #58CC02;\n--color-primary-dark: #46A302;\n--color-surface: #F7F7F7;\n--color-bg: #FFFFFF;\n\n/* Semantic colors */\n--color-success: #58CC02;\n--color-success-bg: #D7F5B1;\n--color-error: #FF4B4B;\n--color-error-bg: #FFD0D0;\n```\n\n### Typography\n\nExtract font families and build the Google Fonts URL:\n\n```html\n<link href=\"https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Nunito:wght@500;600;700&display=swap\" rel=\"stylesheet\" />\n```\n\nMap to CSS custom properties:\n\n```css\n--font-primary: 'Nunito', system-ui, -apple-system, sans-serif;\n\n/* Type scale */\n--text-heading-xl-size: 28px;\n--text-heading-xl-weight: 700;\n--text-heading-xl-lh: 1.2;\n\n--text-body-size: 16px;\n--text-body-weight: 600;\n--text-body-lh: 1.5;\n```\n\n### Spacing\n\n```css\n--space-1: 4px;\n--space-2: 8px;\n--space-3: 12px;\n--space-4: 16px;\n--space-6: 24px;\n--space-8: 32px;\n```\n\n### Border Radius\n\n```css\n--radius-sm: 8px;\n--radius-md: 12px;\n--radius-lg: 16px;\n--radius-pill: 999px;\n```\n\n### Shadows\n\n```css\n--shadow-sm: 0 2px 4px rgba(0,0,0,0.08);\n--shadow-md: 0 4px 12px rgba(0,0,0,0.12);\n--shadow-lg: 0 8px 24px rgba(0,0,0,0.16);\n```\n\n### Motion\n\n```css\n--ease-bounce: cubic-bezier(0.34, 1.56, 0.64, 1);\n--ease-out: cubic-bezier(0, 0, 0.2, 1);\n--duration-fast: 150ms;\n--duration-normal: 250ms;\n--duration-slow: 400ms;\n```\n\n### Device & Safe Areas\n\n```css\n/* Mobile viewport */\n--device-width: 375px;\n--device-height: 812px;\n\n/* Touch targets (Material 3 minimum) */\n--touch-min: 48px;\n\n/* Scaffold chrome heights */\n--app-bar-height: 56px;\n--bottom-nav-height: 80px;\n--status-bar-height: 44px;\n--home-indicator-height: 34px;\n```\n\n## Flutter Token Mapping\n\nThe CSS tokens map to Flutter `AppTheme` constants and Material 3 theme properties:\n\n| CSS Token | Flutter Equivalent |\n|-----------|-------------------|\n| `--color-primary: #hex` | `ColorScheme.fromSeed(seedColor: Color(0xFF...))` |\n| `--color-surface: #hex` | `ColorScheme.surface` |\n| `--font-primary: 'Outfit'` | `GoogleFonts.outfit()` in `TextTheme` |\n| `--radius-md: 12px` | `AppTheme.radiusMd = 12` |\n| `--space-4: 16px` | `AppTheme.spaceMd = 16` |\n| `--ease-bounce: cubic-bezier(...)` | `AppTheme.easeBounce = Cubic(...)` |\n| `--duration-normal: 250ms` | `AppTheme.durationNormal = Duration(milliseconds: 250)` |\n| `--touch-min: 48px` | Material 3 default (48dp minimum tap target) |\n| `--app-bar-height: 56px` | `AppBar` default height |\n| `--bottom-nav-height: 80px` | `NavigationBar` default height |\n","numLines":143,"startLine":1,"totalLines":143}}}
[2026-05-18T15:11:37.055Z] [TOOL_RESULT] 1	# Reading a DESIGN.md
2	
3	How to parse a DESIGN.md file and extract design tokens for mobile screen mockup generation. Tokens are expressed as CSS custom properties for browser preview, but map directly to Flutter's `AppTheme` constants.
4	
5	**Input:** `DESIGN.md` file (project design system)
6	**Output:** `:root` CSS custom properties block (for preview) + Google Fonts `<link>` tag
7	
8	## Section Mapping
9	
10	A DESIGN.md contains up to 12 sections. Each maps to specific CSS custom properties:
11	
12	| DESIGN.md Section | CSS Output | Example |
13	|---|---|---|
14	| **Color Palette** | `--color-{name}: {hex}` | `--color-primary: #58CC02` |
15	| **Typography** | `--font-{role}`, `--text-{size}` + Google Fonts URL | `--font-primary: 'Nunito', sans-serif` |
16	| **Spacing System** | `--space-{n}: {value}` | `--space-4: 16px` |
17	| **Border Radius** | `--radius-{size}: {value}` | `--radius-md: 16px` |
18	| **Shadows & Elevation** | `--shadow-{level}: {value}` | `--shadow-sm: 0 2px 4px rgba(0,0,0,0.08)` |
19	| **Motion & Animation** | `--ease-{name}`, `--duration-{name}` | `--ease-bounce: cubic-bezier(0.34, 1.56, 0.64, 1)` |
20	| **Visual Theme** | Atmosphere dials inform layout density, motion intensity | Used as generation guidance, not direct tokens |
21	| **Component Patterns** | Reference for HTML structure and state classes | Informs element markup |
22	| **Anti-Patterns** | Banned patterns list | Quality gate during generation |
23	| **Device & Safe Areas** | Phone viewport, safe area insets, status bar | `--device-width: 375px`, `--touch-min: 48px` |
24	| **Iconography** | Icon style, stroke width, sizes | Informs inline SVG specs |
25	| **Accessibility** | Contrast, touch targets, motion preferences | Informs ARIA + `prefers-reduced-motion` |
26	
27	## Extraction Rules
28	
29	### Colors
30	
31	For every color entry like `"Leaf Green (#58CC02) — primary action"`:
32	- Use the **token name** from DESIGN.md as the CSS property name
33	- Prefix with `--color-`
34	
35	```css
36	/* From Color Palette table */
37	--color-primary: #58CC02;
38	--color-primary-dark: #46A302;
39	--color-surface: #F7F7F7;
40	--color-bg: #FFFFFF;
41	
42	/* Semantic colors */
43	--color-success: #58CC02;
44	--color-success-bg: #D7F5B1;
45	--color-error: #FF4B4B;
46	--color-error-bg: #FFD0D0;
47	```
48	
49	### Typography
50	
51	Extract font families and build the Google Fonts URL:
52	
53	```html
54	<link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Nunito:wght@500;600;700&display=swap" rel="stylesheet" />
55	```
56	
57	Map to CSS custom properties:
58	
59	```css
60	--font-primary: 'Nunito', system-ui, -apple-system, sans-serif;
61	
62	/* Type scale */
63	--text-heading-xl-size: 28px;
64	--text-heading-xl-weight: 700;
65	--text-heading-xl-lh: 1.2;
66	
67	--text-body-size: 16px;
68	--text-body-weight: 600;
69	--text-body-lh: 1.5;
70	```
71	
72	### Spacing
73	
74	```css
75	--space-1: 4px;
76	--space-2: 8px;
77	--space-3: 12px;
78	--space-4: 16px;
79	--space-6: 24px;
80	--space-8: 32px;
81	```
82	
83	### Border Radius
84	
85	```css
86	--radius-sm: 8px;
87	--radius-md: 12px;
88	--radius-lg: 16px;
89	--radius-pill: 999px;
90	```
91	
92	### Shadows
93	
94	```css
95	--shadow-sm: 0 2px 4px rgba(0,0,0,0.08);
96	--shadow-md: 0 4px 12px rgba(0,0,0,0.12);
97	--shadow-lg: 0 8px 24px rgba(0,0,0,0.16);
98	```
99	
100	### Motion
101	
102	```css
103	--ease-bounce: cubic-bezier(0.34, 1.56, 0.64, 1);
104	--ease-out: cubic-bezier(0, 0, 0.2, 1);
105	--duration-fast: 150ms;
106	--duration-normal: 250ms;
107	--duration-slow: 400ms;
108	```
109	
110	### Device & Safe Areas
111	
112	```css
113	/* Mobile viewport */
114	--device-width: 375px;
115	--device-height: 812px;
116	
117	/* Touch targets (Material 3 minimum) */
118	--touch-min: 48px;
119	
120	/* Scaffold chrome heights */
121	--app-bar-height: 56px;
122	--bottom-nav-height: 80px;
123	--status-bar-height: 44px;
124	--home-indicator-height: 34px;
125	```
126	
127	## Flutter Token Mapping
128	
129	The CSS tokens map to Flutter `AppTheme` constants and Material 3 theme properties:
130	
131	| CSS Token | Flutter Equivalent |
132	|-----------|-------------------|
133	| `--color-primary: #hex` | `ColorScheme.fromSeed(seedColor: Color(0xFF...))` |
134	| `--color-surface: #hex` | `ColorScheme.surface` |
135	| `--font-primary: 'Outfit'` | `GoogleFonts.outfit()` in `TextTheme` |
136	| `--radius-md: 12px` | `AppTheme.radiusMd = 12` |
137	| `--space-4: 16px` | `AppTheme.spaceMd = 16` |
138	| `--ease-bounce: cubic-bezier(...)` | `AppTheme.easeBounce = Cubic(...)` |
139	| `--duration-normal: 250ms` | `AppTheme.durationNormal = Duration(milliseconds: 250)` |
140	| `--touch-min: 48px` | Material 3 default (48dp minimum tap target) |
141	| `--app-bar-height: 56px` | `AppBar` default height |
142	| `--bottom-nav-height: 80px` | `NavigationBar` default height |
