[2026-05-18T15:11:37.057Z] [TOOL_RESULT] 1	# Pregnant Tracker - Baby Bump: Product Requirements Document
2	
3	## Overview
4	
5	Pregnant Tracker - Baby Bump is a wellness-focused mobile app designed to help expecting mothers stay healthy, relaxed, and confident throughout every stage of pregnancy. It combines cycle tracking, pregnancy progress monitoring, nutrition management, and mindfulness tools in a single private companion that keeps all data on-device. The app delivers a calming, nurturing experience that empowers mothers with trusted educational content and practical daily health management tools.
6	
7	## User Personas
8	
9	### First-Time Expecting Mothers
10	Women experiencing pregnancy for the first time who need guidance on what to expect at each stage. They seek reassurance, week-by-week progress updates, and easy-to-understand educational content about maternal care and body changes.
11	
12	**Key Goals:**
13	- Understand what is happening at each stage of pregnancy
14	- Feel reassured and supported with trusted information
15	- Track due date and milestones
16	
17	### Health-Conscious Mothers
18	Mothers who actively monitor their weight, nutrition, and exercise throughout pregnancy. They value data, progress charts, and actionable health insights.
19	
20	**Key Goals:**
21	- Track weight changes and nutrition intake over time
22	- Follow safe exercise and kegel routines
23	- View clear progress charts and daily logs
24	
25	### Anxiety-Prone Mothers
26	Expecting mothers who experience heightened stress or emotional changes during pregnancy. They benefit from mindfulness tools, breathing exercises, and mood tracking to manage pregnancy-related anxiety.
27	
28	**Key Goals:**
29	- Access breathing and relaxation exercises on demand
30	- Log moods and energy levels to identify emotional patterns
31	- Receive gentle recommendations for stress relief
32	
33	## Features
34	
35	### Reproductive Health & Cycle Tracking
36	Track menstrual cycles, ovulation predictions, and fertile window estimates. Log irregular cycles and receive reminders.
37	
38	**Acceptance Criteria:**
39	- User can log menstrual cycle start and end dates
40	- App calculates and displays ovulation predictions and fertile windows
41	- User can mark irregular cycles and add notes
42	- Reminders can be set for cycle-related events
43	
44	### Weight & Nutrition Management
45	Track pregnancy weight changes with charts and daily logs. Receive nutrition and hydration tips tailored for each pregnancy stage.
46	
47	**Acceptance Criteria:**
48	- User can log daily weight entries
49	- Weight progress is displayed in a simple chart over time
50	- Nutrition and hydration tips update based on current pregnancy week
51	- User can view historical weight data
52	
53	### Pregnancy Progress & Self-Care
54	Calculate due date, view weekly updates on body changes, and access guidance on safe exercises, kegel routines, and daily self-care reminders.
55	
56	**Acceptance Criteria:**
57	- User can set a due date or calculate it from last menstrual period
58	- Weekly updates describe current body changes and baby development
59	- Safe exercise and kegel routine guides are available per trimester
60	- Daily self-care reminders can be enabled or disabled
61	
62	### Stress Relief & Mindfulness
63	Breathing tips, light stretching guides, and mindful activities for managing stress and emotional changes.
64	
65	**Acceptance Criteria:**
66	- At least one guided breathing exercise is available
67	- Light stretching routines are provided with clear instructions
68	- Mindful activity suggestions are accessible from the main navigation
69	
70	### Health Organization & Daily Management
71	Note doctor visits, track symptoms, and save reminders for upcoming checkups in a single secure place.
72	
73	**Acceptance Criteria:**
74	- User can create, edit, and delete doctor visit notes
75	- Symptoms can be logged with date and severity
76	- Reminders can be scheduled for upcoming checkups
77	- All data is stored securely on-device
78	
79	### Emotional & Behavioral Wellness
80	Log moods, energy levels, and symptoms to understand emotional patterns. Receive gentle recommendations for relaxation and positivity.
81	
82	**Acceptance Criteria:**
83	- User can log mood and energy level daily
84	- Emotional patterns are visualized over time
85	- Gentle wellness recommendations are shown based on logged data
86	
87	### Educational Health Content
88	Trusted educational resources about maternal care, pregnancy nutrition, and body changes with medically reviewed, easy-to-understand content.
89	
90	**Acceptance Criteria:**
91	- Educational articles are organized by topic (nutrition, body changes, maternal care)
92	- Content is presented in easy-to-read format
93	- Content is accessible offline
94	
95	## Non-Functional Requirements
96	
97	### Performance
98	- Smooth 60fps animations and chart transitions throughout the app
99	- App launches and is interactive promptly on mid-range devices
100	- Charts and data views render without perceptible lag
101	
102	### Privacy & Data Storage
103	- Offline-first architecture with all user data stored on-device
104	- No user data transmitted to external servers
105	- Data persists across app restarts
106	
107	### Platform & Layout
108	- Built with Flutter and Material 3 theming
109	- Mobile-only, portrait orientation, phone-optimized layout
110	- Consistent experience across iOS and Android
111	
112	### Accessibility
113	- Full screen reader support for all interactive elements
114	- Dynamic type support for user-preferred font sizes
115	- Reduced motion mode that disables non-essential animations
116	
