[2026-05-18T15:11:37.058Z] [TOOL_RESULT] 1	# Pregnant Tracker - Baby Bump
2	
3	## Purpose
4	
5	Pregnant Tracker - Baby Bump is a wellness-focused mobile app designed to help expecting mothers stay healthy, relaxed, and confident throughout every stage of pregnancy. It combines cycle tracking, pregnancy progress monitoring, nutrition management, and mindfulness tools in a single private companion that keeps all data on-device.
6	
7	## Core Features
8	
9	- **Reproductive Health & Cycle Tracking** — Menstrual tracking, ovulation predictions, and fertile window estimates. Log irregular cycles and receive reminders to understand reproductive rhythm
10	- **Weight & Nutrition Management** — Track pregnancy weight changes with simple charts and daily logs. Nutrition and hydration tips tailored for each pregnancy stage
11	- **Pregnancy Progress & Self-Care** — Due date calculation, weekly updates on body changes, guidance on safe exercises, kegel routines, and daily self-care reminders
12	- **Stress Relief & Mindfulness** — Breathing tips, light stretching, and mindful activities for managing stress and emotional changes naturally
13	- **Health Organization & Daily Management** — Note doctor visits, track symptoms, and save reminders for upcoming checkups in a single secure place
14	- **Emotional & Behavioral Wellness** — Log moods, energy levels, and symptoms to understand emotional patterns. Gentle recommendations for relaxation and positivity
15	- **Educational Health Content** — Trusted educational resources about maternal care, pregnancy nutrition, and body changes with medically reviewed, easy-to-understand content
16	
17	## Target Audience
18	
19	- **First-Time Expecting Mothers** — Need guidance on what to expect at each stage, want reassurance and educational content
20	- **Health-Conscious Mothers** — Track weight, nutrition, and exercise throughout pregnancy, value data and progress charts
21	- **Anxiety-Prone Mothers** — Benefit from mindfulness tools, breathing exercises, and mood tracking to manage pregnancy-related stress
22	
23	## Visual Direction
24	
25	- Soft, nurturing pastel palette with lavender and blush tones
26	- Warm and calming atmosphere that conveys care and safety
27	- Illustrated fetal-development scenes and fruit-size baby comparisons
28	- Spacious layout with generous whitespace for emotional calm
29	- Gentle spring-based animations that reinforce a sense of softness
30	
31	## Technical Requirements
32	
33	- Flutter with Material 3 theming
34	- Offline-first with all data stored on-device for privacy
35	- Mobile-only (portrait, phone-optimized)
36	- Smooth 60fps animations and chart transitions
37	- Accessible (screen reader support, dynamic type, reduced motion)
38	
